title: Freeze Dried Cat Nibbles CHICKEN DIET FOR CATS | Northwest Naturals
descriptions: We use the same meats found at your finest natural food stores. All of our muscle and organ meats are chopped (not ground) partially frozen at the time of processing to ensure the availability of the highest quality nutrients, then individually quick frozen to keep the integrity of the ingredient quality.
Our recipes are very simple: muscle meat, organ meats and natural raw ground bone, all from the same species. No added fruits or vegetables. A true carnivore diet!
key_benefits: Freeze Dried Diets in the perfect cat size nibbles
Pour and feed straight from the bag
Always make sure water is available with any freeze dried foods
Shelf life for freeze dried is 2 years unopened – 1-2 mos. if stored properly after opening
Complete and Balanced Diets can also be used for treats or as a topper
All poultry products are HPP’d for product and food handling safety
Highest quality  muscle and organ meats
Chicken, Duck, Turkey and Whitefish – Sourced in the USA.  Rabbit sourced in France.
No Added Hormones and Antibiotic Free – Federal regulations prohibit the use of hormones in poultry.
2 sizes for added convenience
ingredients: Chicken, Chicken Necks, Chicken Hearts, Chicken Liver, Egg, Gelatin, Water, Dulse Powder, Dried Kelp, Ground Flaxseed, Organic Psyllium Husk Powder, Salmon Oil, Inulin, Potassium Chloride, Sodium Chloride, Taurine, Vitamin B Supplement, Copper Proteinate, Manganese Proteinate, Vitamin E Supplement, Copper Proteinate, Mixed Tocopherols (as preservative). Vitamin D3 Supplement.
